attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles a table. The instructor tells him that you can start disassembling. The student unscrews multiple hex socket heads, and he disassembles the fourth legs one by one. He disassembles the shelf and the top table. Finally he collects all the hex socket heads.

attributes.Transcription: You can start to disassemble it.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrews the hex socket heads that are on the shelf.
The student unscrews the hex socket heads on the top of the table.
The student disassembles the first leg of the furniture.
The student disassembles the second leg of the furniture.
The student disassembles the third leg of the furniture.
The student disassembles the top table.
The student disassembles the fourth leg and the shelf.
